{"type": "article", "id": 25822, "title": "自行车后货架装载系统", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-22T07:12:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122602rUzE8uB90dlLQpDP.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这个颠覆了一般自行车后货架装载系统名为 TPack，由台湾的<a href=\"http://www.freeparable.com/tw\">浮力森林设计</a>出品，是一个时尚大方的储物解决方式。系统包含：后架（TRack）、背包（TCase）和篮袋（TBasket），其中背包既可以当作日常单肩包使用也可以用作车袋，篮袋以防水布料制成并做了束口设计防止物品掉落。这个系统还采用了粘扣带和安全扣的双重保险，为可能遇到的恶劣路况做好了准备。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.zeczec.com/projects/bikebag-basket\">链接</a>参与众筹。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122600I3F6BvJL49OT0xZX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122600AwuxO0ZaPFLKzpg4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071226018qenzbPCAt7SF6mD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64756447\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122601HeawNDLGoS4JXC7u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.475\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n\n\n"}